---
title: Cheddar-Stuffed Meatloaves with Potato Wedges, Asparagus, Crispy Shallot & Special Sauce
description: You probably perk up at “cheddar-stuffed anything.” (We do too.) But, cheddar-stuffed meatloaves? Cheese turns melty inside beef, then loaves are topped with more cheddar, drizzled with special sauce, and sprinkled with homemade crispy fried shallot. On the side, roasted potato wedges are served with sautéed carrots and more special sauce for dipping.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/63fe19ea14b50b5a100da379-762e6d3f.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/6595d035050f2b642e9a301b.pdf
nutrition:
